 {{ill|Hyogo Prefecture|ja|兵庫県}} ** {{ill|Yumura Onsen (Hyogo)|lt=Yumura Onsen (Hyogo)|lt=Yumura Onsen Fire Festival|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント}} * {{ill|Tottori Prefecture|ja|鳥取県}} ** {{ill|Tottori Shan-Shan Festival|ja|鳥取しゃんしゃん祭}} * {{ill|Tokushima Prefecture|ja|徳島県}} ** {{ill|Awa Odori|ja|阿波踊り}} – Its {{ill|Tokushima City Awa Odori|ja|徳島市阿波おどり}} is one of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|ja|四国三大祭り}}. * {{ill|Kochi Prefecture|ja|高知県}} ** {{ill|Yosakoi Festival|ja|よさこい祭り}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Shikoku. * {{ill|Fukuoka Prefecture|ja|福岡県}} ** {{ill|Hakata Gion Yamakasa|ja|博多祇園山笠}} * {{ill|Kumamoto Prefecture|ja|熊本県}} ** {{ill|Yamaga Lantern Festival|ja|山鹿灯籠まつり}} * {{ill|Miyazaki Prefecture|ja|宮崎県}} ** {{ill|Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|ja|都城六月灯おかげ祭り}}
