** {{ill|Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|ja|都城六月灯おかげ祭り}}

== Summer Festivals Outside Japan ==
* {{ill|Sabantuy|ja|サバントゥイ}} – A summer festival held along the middle reaches of the {{ill|Volga River|ja|ヴォルガ川}} in {{ill|Russia|ja|ロシア}}.

