* {{ill|Parades|ja|パレード|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Parades|qq=}}
* {{ill|Fireworks|ja|花火大会|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fireworks|qq=}}
* {{ill|Yatai|ja|屋台|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yatai|qq=}} (food stalls, often at {{ill|Ennichi|ja|縁日|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ennichi|qq=}})
* {{ill|Matsuri float|lt=Matsuri float|lt=Floats|ja|山車|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Floats|qq=}} and {{ill|Festival music|ja|祭囃子|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Festival music|qq=}}
* Events using temporary stages:
** Song shows
** Character shows (often featuring {{ill|Anime|ja|アニメ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Anime|qq=}}, {{ill|Super Sentai|ja|戦隊シリーズ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Super Sentai|qq=}}, or {{ill|Local hero (Japan)|ja|ローカルヒーロー|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Local hero (Japan)|qq=}})
** {{ill|Magic (illusion)|ja|奇術|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Magic (illusion)|qq=}} shows
** {{ill|Karaoke|ja|カラオケ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Karaoke|qq=}} competitions

