araji Festival|ja|福島わらじまつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukushima Waraji Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Gunma Prefecture|Gunma Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Kiryu Yagibushi Festival|ja|桐生八木節まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiryu Yagibushi Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Tokyo|Tokyo]] ** [[:en:Fukagawa Matsuri|Fukagawa Matsuri]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Edo|ja|江戸三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Edo|qq=}}. * [[:en:Ishikawa Prefecture|Ishikawa Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Iida-machi Toro-yama Festival|ja|飯田町燈籠山祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iida-machi Toro-yama Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Gifu Prefecture|Gifu Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Gujo Odori|ja|郡上踊り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gujo Odori|qq=}} * [[:en:Aichi Prefecture|Aichi Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Tenno Matsuri|Owari Tsushima Tennō Festival]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great River Festivals of Japan|ja|日本三大川祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great River Festivals of Japan|qq=}}. * [[:en:Kyoto Prefecture|Kyoto Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Gion Matsuri|Gion Matsuri]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Japan|ja|日本三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Japan|qq=}}. * [[:en:Osaka Prefecture|Osaka Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Tenjin Matsuri|Tenjin Matsuri]] – Part of the Three Great Festivals of Japan and the {{ill|Three Great Summer Festivals of Osaka|ja|大阪三大夏祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Summer Festivals of Osaka|qq=}}. * [[:en:Hyōgo Prefecture|Hyōgo Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yumura Onsen (Hyōgo)|lt=Yumura Onsen (Hyōgo)|lt=Yumura Onsen Fire Festival|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yumura Onsen (Hyōgo)|qq=}} * [[:en:Tottori Prefecture|Tottori Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Shan-shan festival|Tottori Shan-Shan Festival]] * [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Awa Dance Festival|Awa Odori]] – Its {{ill|Tokushima City Awa Odori|ja|徳島市阿波おどり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokushima City Awa Odori|qq=}} is one of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|ja|四国三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|qq=}}. * [[:en:Kōchi Prefecture|Kochi Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yosakoi Festival|ja|よさこい祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yosakoi Festival|qq=}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Shikoku. * [[:en:Fukuoka Prefecture|Fukuoka Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Hakata Gion Yamakasa|Hakata Gion Yamakasa]] * [[:en:Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yamaga Lantern Festival|ja|山鹿灯籠まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamaga Lantern Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Miyazaki Prefecture|Miyazaki Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|ja|都城六月灯おかげ祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|qq=}}
