12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokushima City Awa Odori|qq=}} is one of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|ja|四国三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|qq=}}. * [[:en:Kōchi Prefecture|Kochi Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yosakoi Festival|ja|よさこい祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yosakoi Festival|qq=}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Shikoku. * [[:en:Fukuoka Prefecture|Fukuoka Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Hakata Gion Yamakasa|Hakata Gion Yamakasa]] * [[:en:Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yamaga Lantern Festival|ja|山鹿灯籠まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamaga Lantern Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Miyazaki Prefecture|Miyazaki Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|ja|都城六月灯おかげ祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|qq=}}
