=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 仙台七夕}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Tohoku. * [[:en:Akita Prefecture|Akita Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Akita Kantō|ja|秋田竿燈まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanto Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 竿燈}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Tohoku. * [[:en:Fukushima Prefecture|Fukushima Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Fukushima Waraji Festival|ja|福島わらじまつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukushima Waraji Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Gunma Prefecture|Gunma Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Kiryu Yagibushi Festival|ja|桐生八木節まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiryu Yagibushi Festival|qq=|1=Kiryū Yagibushi festival|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11537271}} * [[:en:Tokyo|Tokyo]] ** [[:en:Fukagawa Matsuri|Fukagawa Matsuri]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Edo|ja|江戸三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Edo|qq=}}. * [[:en:Ishikawa Prefecture|Ishikawa Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Iida-machi Toro-yama Festival|ja|飯田町燈籠山祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iida-machi Toro-yama Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Gifu Prefecture|Gifu Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Gujo Odori|ja|郡上踊り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gujo Odori|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 郡上おどり|1=Gujō Odori|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q6430768}} * [[:en:Aichi Prefecture|Aichi Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Tenno Matsuri|Owari Tsushima Tennō Festival]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great River Festivals of Japan|ja|日本三大川祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great River Festivals of Japan|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. * [[:en:Kyoto Prefecture|Kyoto Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Gion Matsuri|Gion Matsuri]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Japan|ja|日本三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Japan|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 日本三大一覧|1=Japan's Top 3|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10311536}}. * [[:en:Osaka Prefecture|Osaka Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Tenjin Matsuri|Tenjin Matsuri]] – P