== Representative Summer Festivals of Japan == [[File:Aomori Nebuta Festival Float August 2006.jpg|thumb|180px|{{ill|Aomori Nebuta Festival|ja|青森ねぶた祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aomori Nebuta Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 青森ねぶた|1=Aomori Nebuta Matsuri|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q862407}}]] [[File:Sendai Tanabata Festival 2010.jpg|thumb|180px|{{ill|Sendai Tanabata Festival|ja|仙台七夕まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sendai Tanabata Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 仙台七夕}}]] [[File:Tomioka hachimangu10.jpg|thumb|180px|[[:en:Fukagawa Matsuri|Fukagawa Matsuri]]]] [[File:Gion Matsuri 2017-5.jpg|thumb|180px|[[:en:Gion Matsuri|Gion Matsuri]]]] [[File:Awa-odori 2008 Tokushima.jpg|thumb|180px|[[:en:Awa Dance Festival|Awa Odori]]]] * [[:en:Hokkaido|Hokkaido]] ** {{ill|Ubagami Daijingu Togyo Festival|ja|姥神大神宮渡御祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ubagami Daijingu Togyo Festival|qq=}} ** {{ill|Hakodate Port Festival|ja|函館港まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hakodate Port Festival|qq=}} – Features dances like the {{ill|Squid Dance|ja|いか踊り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Squid Dance|qq=}}. * [[:en:Aomori Prefecture|Aomori Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Aomori Nebuta Festival|ja|青森ねぶた祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Aomori Nebuta Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 青森ねぶた|1=Aomori Nebuta Matsuri|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q862407}} – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Tohoku|lt=Three Great Festivals of Tohoku|lt=Three Great Festivals of Tohoku|ja|東北三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Tohoku|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Hirosaki Neputa Matsuri|lt=Hirosaki Neputa Matsuri|lt=Hirosaki Neputa Festival|ja|弘前ねぷたまつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirosaki Neputa Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 弘前ねぷた}} * [[:en:Miyagi Prefecture|Miyagi Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Sendai Tanabata Festival|ja|仙台七夕まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sendai Tanabata Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 仙台七夕}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Tohoku. * [[:en:Akita Prefecture|Akita Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Akita Kantō|ja|秋田竿燈まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanto Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 竿燈}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Tohoku. * [[:en:Fukushima Prefecture|Fukushima Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Fukushima Waraji Festival|ja|福島わらじまつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukushima Waraji Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Gunma Prefecture|Gunma Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Kiryu Yagibushi Festival|ja|桐生八木節まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiryu Yagibushi Festival|qq=|1=Kiryū Yagibushi festival|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11537271}} * [[:en:Tokyo|Tokyo]] ** [[:en:Fukagawa Matsuri|Fukagawa Matsuri]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Edo|ja|江戸三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Edo|qq=}}. * [[:en:Ishikawa Prefecture|Ishikawa Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Iida-machi Toro-yama Festival|ja|飯田町燈籠山祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iida-machi Toro-yama Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Gifu Prefecture|Gifu Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Gujo Odori|ja|郡上踊り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gujo Odori|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 郡上おどり|1=Gujō Odori|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q6430768}} * [[:en:Aichi Prefecture|Aichi Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Tenno Matsuri|Owari Tsushima Tennō Festival]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great River Festivals of Japan|ja|日本三大川祭|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great River Festivals of Japan|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. * [[:en:Kyoto Prefecture|Kyoto Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Gion Matsuri|Gion Matsuri]] – One of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Japan|ja|日本三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Japan|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 日本三大一覧|1=Japan's Top 3|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q10311536}}. * [[:en:Osaka Prefecture|Osaka Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Tenjin Matsuri|Tenjin Matsuri]] – Part of the Three Great Festivals of Japan and the {{ill|Three Great Summer Festivals of Osaka|ja|大阪三大夏祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Summer Festivals of Osaka|qq=}}. * [[:en:Hyōgo Prefecture|Hyōgo Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yumura Onsen (Hyōgo)|lt=Yumura Onsen (Hyōgo)|lt=Yumura Onsen Fire Festival|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|ja|湯村温泉 (兵庫県)#イベント|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yumura Onsen (Hyōgo)|qq=|1=Yumura Onsen|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q8061163}} * [[:en:Tottori Prefecture|Tottori Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Shan-shan festival|Tottori Shan-Shan Festival]] * [[:en:Tokushima Prefecture|Tokushima Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Awa Dance Festival|Awa Odori]] – Its {{ill|Tokushima City Awa Odori|ja|徳島市阿波おどり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokushima City Awa Odori|qq=}} is one of the {{ill|Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|ja|四国三大祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Three Great Festivals of Shikoku|qq=}}. * [[:en:Kōchi Prefecture|Kochi Prefecture]] ** {{ill|YOSAKOI Festival|ja|よさこい祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/YOSAKOI Festival|qq=}} – One of the Three Great Festivals of Shikoku. * [[:en:Fukuoka Prefecture|Fukuoka Prefecture]] ** [[:en:Hakata Gion Yamakasa|Hakata Gion Yamakasa]] * [[:en:Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Yamaga Lantern Festival|ja|山鹿灯籠まつり|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamaga Lantern Festival|qq=}} * [[:en:Miyazaki Prefecture|Miyazaki Prefecture]] ** {{ill|Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|ja|都城六月灯おかげ祭り|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Miyakonojo Rokugatsudo Okage Festival|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}
